1. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper deals with the problem of achieving reliable communication over a relay network, which is a classic problem in information theory. 
2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on relay networks, which are a key component of modern communication networks. 
3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper deals with the problem of communication over networks, which is a topic of interest in social and information networks. 
4. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - The paper may involve computational complexity analysis of the achievable rate and capacity bounds. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper may involve the transmission of multimedia data over the relay network, which is a topic of interest in multimedia communication.
